# Status high-level only

- **project-status.md** (`docs/state-snapshotter-rework/operations/project-status.md`) is **high-level only**.
- Do NOT keep there: long archives, detailed stage-by-stage implementation notes, full test plan, spec/design/testing copy.
- Do keep: stage status table, short implemented summary, in progress, planned, blockers. Everything detailed belongs in spec/, design/, testing/, adr/.
